body_html:
Hmm - technically, you cannot do that. You can feed_dict into a placeholder. Then that can go into a queue. This holds up for anything, so also for the Dataset API:
https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r1.3/programmers_guide/datasets
The dataset API can be feedable, just like a queue.

body:
Hmm - technically, you cannot do that. You can feed_dict into a placeholder. Then _that_ can go into a queue. This holds up for anything, so also for the Dataset API:
https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r1.3/programmers_guide/datasets
The dataset API can be _feedable_, just like a queue.
